---
import GuideLayout from "@/layouts/GuideLayout.astro";

const title = "Knowledge Base";
const description = "Learn how to manage and optimize your knowledge base for better assistant responses";
---

<GuideLayout title={title} description={description}>
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Knowledge Base</h1>

        <p class="text-lg mb-12">
            The Knowledge Base is a central repository for all the information your IntelliSync assistant needs to provide accurate and contextual responses. By properly managing your knowledge base, you can ensure your assistant delivers consistent and helpful information to your users.
        </p>

        <section class="mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6">Adding Content</h2>
            <div class="space-y-4">
                <p>There are several ways to import content into your knowledge base:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                    <li>
                        <strong>Direct Upload:</strong> Upload PDF files directly through the interface
                        <span class="inline-flex items-center px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-medium bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 ml-2">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-3.5 w-3.5 mr-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                            </svg>
                            DOC, DOCX, TXT coming soon
                        </span>
                    </li>
                    <li><strong>URL Import:</strong> Import content from web pages by providing URLs</li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>API Integration:</strong> Use our REST API to programmatically add content
                        <span class="inline-flex items-center px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-medium bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 ml-2">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-3.5 w-3.5 mr-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                            </svg>
                            Coming Soon
                        </span>
                    </li>
                    <li><strong>Manual Entry:</strong> Create and edit content directly in the knowledge base editor</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="mt-4">Each piece of content is automatically processed and indexed for optimal retrieval by your assistant.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6">Content Organization</h2>
            <div class="space-y-4">
                <p>Organize your knowledge base effectively using these features:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                    <li><strong>Collections:</strong> Group related content into collections for better management</li>
                    <li><strong>Tags:</strong> Add metadata tags to improve searchability and categorization</li>
                    <li><strong>Hierarchical Structure:</strong> Create parent-child relationships between content pieces</li>
                    <li><strong>Custom Categories:</strong> Define your own organizational structure based on your needs</li>
                </ul>
                <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-500 p-4 mt-4">
                    <p class="text-sm"> <strong>Pro Tip:</strong> Use a consistent naming convention for collections and tags to maintain clarity as your knowledge base grows.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6">Content Types</h2>
            <div class="space-y-4">
                <p>IntelliSync supports various content types to accommodate different information needs:</p>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                    <div class="border rounded-lg p-4">
                        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Documentation</h3>
                        <ul class="list-disc pl-4 space-y-1">
                            <li>API documentation</li>
                            <li>User guides</li>
                            <li>Technical specifications</li>
                            <li>Process documentation</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="border rounded-lg p-4">
                        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Knowledge Articles</h3>
                        <ul class="list-disc pl-4 space-y-1">
                            <li>How-to guides</li>
                            <li>FAQs</li>
                            <li>Best practices</li>
                            <li>Troubleshooting guides</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6">Search and Retrieval</h2>
            <div class="space-y-4">
                <p>Understanding how your assistant searches the knowledge base:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                    <li><strong>Semantic Search:</strong> Uses AI to understand the context and meaning of queries</li>
                    <li><strong>Relevance Scoring:</strong> Ranks content based on relevance to the user's question</li>
                    <li><strong>Context Window:</strong> Maintains conversation context for more accurate responses</li>
                    <li><strong>Citation:</strong> Automatically cites sources when providing information</li>
                </ul>
                <div class="bg-yellow-100 border-l-4 border-yellow-500 p-4 mt-4">
                    <p class="text-sm text-yellow-950"> <strong class="text-yellow-950 font-semibold">Note:</strong> The quality of search results depends heavily on how well your content is structured and tagged.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6">Maintenance</h2>
            <div class="space-y-4">
                <p>Regular maintenance ensures your knowledge base remains accurate and useful:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                    <li><strong>Content Review:</strong> Schedule regular reviews of existing content</li>
                    <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> Monitor which content is most frequently accessed</li>
                    <li><strong>Update Tracking:</strong> Keep track of when content was last updated</li>
                    <li><strong>Quality Metrics:</strong> Track assistant response accuracy and user feedback</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="mt-4">Set up automated notifications for content that needs review based on age or usage patterns.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6">
                Version Control
                <span class="inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 ml-2">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 mr-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                    </svg>
                    Coming Soon
                </span>
            </h2>
            <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-500 p-4">
                <div class="flex">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                        <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7-4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zM9 9a1 1 0 000 2v3a1 1 0 001 1h1a1 1 0 100-2v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H9z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div class="ml-3">
                        <p class="text-sm text-blue-700">
                            Version control features are currently in development. Soon you'll be able to track changes, manage versions, and collaborate on your knowledge base content more effectively.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 border-l-4 border-gray-500 p-4 mt-8">
            <p class="text-gray-700">A well-maintained knowledge base is crucial for your AI Assistant's performance. Regular updates, proper organization, and careful monitoring of content quality will ensure your assistant provides the most accurate and helpful responses to your users.</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mt-2">Need help? Contact our support team for guidance on optimizing your knowledge base.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</GuideLayout>
